AgentMe is a humanoid AI agent that assists in virtual and real-world tasks.

AgentMe is your personal AGI agent within a gamified training platform, designed to evolve through interaction and assist both in virtual worlds and the real world. Create and develop your own AgentMe to enhance your in-game experience while automating real-world tasks using tools like social media, email, and web services. Unlike traditional AI, AgentMe doesn't just chat; it observes simulated environments and takes action based on its surroundings.

Powered by the cutting-edge Spatial Large Action Model (S-LAM), AgentMe is a humanoid interface that runs on the fully decentralized HyperAGI blockchain (https://hyperagi.network).
